snippet.title: Retromancer Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Retromancer is a frantic, fantasy themed twin-stick shooter with a stylish, chunky pixel aesthetic and 4 distinct playable characters.

Retromancer will be available June 6 2019, and you can wishlist it on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1007180/Retromancer/

Also, don't forget to give this video a thumbs up if you liked how the game is looking and subscribe to the Spinfoam Games YouTube channel for more Retromancer videos!
